BayPHP 0.1
Bayfiles PHP library for Bayfiles API v1 Beta

This software is distributed under the MIT license. See LICENSE for more
information.


Please fork me at https://github.com/mcdooda/BayPHP

This library provides access to the bayfiles API through bay\Account and
bay\File classes.

See examples/ for code examples.
See documentation/ for the doxygen documention.

Dependencies:
- pecl http

Incoming updates:
- support for uploading files
- support for re-logging in when the timeout expires
- support for deleting a file by requesting the deleteToken before
- support for easing the use of the Account class as a $_SESSION
- better documentation
- more examples

